            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:88:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/88/5439",
        "text": [
          " : \"اَلْكَفَنُ مِنْ جَمِيعِ اَلْمَالِ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5439 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Abdullah ibn Sinan from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), who said:\n\"The shroud (for burial) is to be provided from the entirety of the wealth (of the deceased).\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2437,
