        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:88:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/88/5440",
        "text": [
          " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كَفَنُ اَلْمَرْأَةِ عَلَى زَوْجِهَا إِذَا مَاتَتْ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5440 - And Imam (as) said:\n\"The shroud of a woman is the responsibility of her husband if she passes away.\"\n[CHAPER=CHAPTER 88 - CHAPTER ON A MAN WHO DIES WHILE OWING A DEBT EQUAL TO PRICE OF HIS SHROUD]\nبَابُ الرَّجُلِ يَمُوتُ وَ عَلَيْهِ دَيْنٌ بِقَدْرِ ثَمَنِ كَفَنِهِ‌"
          ]
        }
      },
